00:46:30,080 --> 00:46:43,220
Rym: Scott did not play, but there are two games that are kind of famous in our circle, because they're both games that we played a reasonable number of times back in college, but Scott and I are mutually, independently undefeated at both of them.

799
00:46:43,921 --> 00:46:48,520
Rym: I am undefeated at Pizarro, and Scott is undefeated at Web of Power, despite many plays.

